snippet: LEEDS--Dalia B. Congregation Emanu-El of the City of New York records with deep sorrow the death of our cherished member, Dalia Leeds. To her family and loved ones we express our profound sympathy. The beautiful qualities of her life shall endure forever in the hearts of those she loved and those who loved her. 1/3
lead_paragraph: LEEDS--Dalia B. Congregation Emanu-El of the City of New York records with deep sorrow the death of our cherished member, Dalia Leeds.
